    <p>In the compose message window, you can:</p>
<ul>
<li>Add recipients [1]</li>
<li>Type a message [2]</li>
<li>Attach files or media [3]</li>
<li>Click the <strong>Send</strong> button [4]</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: You cannot change the course or the subject line if you are forwarding a message.</p>
